A rapid increase in the rodent population in the South Atlantic Autonomous
Region/Nueva Guinea area (as well as Jinotega) has been reported nearly a
year ago. See the following web site:
<http://www.americas.org/news/nir/19990916_rats_hit_atlantic_coast.asp>
